Quarter, core and thinly slice the @apple{1}(quartered, cored and thinly sliced) (peeling optional).

Share the @yoghurt{220%g} between two #serving bowls{}.

Top the yoghurt with the @blueberries{125%g} and apple slices.

Scatter the @granola{120%g} over the fruit.

Drizzle over the @honey{2%sachets} and @ground cinnamon{1/2%sachet} to finish.